==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Bisque
<hw>Bisque</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <def>A point taken by the
receiver of odds in the game of tennis; also, an extra innings allowed
to a weaker player in croquet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bisque</ent>⟦br⟧
